name: FunnyQuoter
0:
”Alexa, ask Funny Quoter to tell me a quote.”
”Alexa, tell Funny Quoter to make me smile.”
”Alexa, tell Funny Quoter to cheer me up.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny quoter
des:
Need a quick laugh? Just ask Alexa! Our Funny Quoter skill combines thousands of knee-slapping puns, zingers, and one liners with the convenience of Amazon’s Echo for a fun and easy way to have a chuckle!

We up the fun by adding real human voices to our jokes! No more monotonous, droning, robotic sounds!

All you have to do is say “Alexa, tell Funny Quoter to make me smile” or “Tell Funny Quoter to cheer me up! And voila! You will hear a joke so outrageously funny that you will be immobilized with laughter!
